HEADWORD: Colloped
<hw>Col"loped</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Having ridges or
bunches of flesh, like collops.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>With that red, gaunt, and <qex>colloped</qex> neck astrain.</q>
<rj><qau>R. Browning.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

